channel.title: Dupe (Same Account Twice)
channel.description:
Ok, well here is a video of the dupe. Just so I am not called a idiot trying to explain. :P I fixed every dupe(I think), but that one. :(
Keep in mind I probly need something that checks if the same name is on(or Ip is on) in the boolean process.
Note: I already tired multi-login, but since you log in at the same exact time, it misses the command.

Thanks. ~ Ed
